author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Session Vault unlocks never-before seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio.

Check out the full three-song session of @liannelahavas from 2015 on our Youtube channel.
title: Lianne La Havas plays "Wonderful" in 2015 #LianneLaHavas

author: The Current
description: Ian Richard Devaney of Nation of Language talks about the ironic nature of band’s song “Inept Apollo” connecting with so many listeners.
title: @NationofLanguage talks about their song "Inept Apollo" and imposter syndrome #interview #shorts

author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session of Cold War Kids featuring previously unreleased footage, from when they visited The Current studio back in 2013.

00:02:37 Miracle Mile
00:05:39 Tuxedos
